parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine head gasket failure can cause engine damage, overheating, and stalling, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Engine timing chain failure can cause engine damage, stalling, and loss of power, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Engine oil leaks can cause engine damage, overheating, and stalling, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
Transmission problems can cause stalling, loss of power, and difficulty shifting gears, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle jumping while shifting into drive

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Vehicle fires can cause damage to the vehicle and surrounding property, and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
The failure of the torque converter solenoid can cause the vehicle to stall, potentially leading to accidents or fatalities, especially in intersections.
Internal transmission failures can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or lock up in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the transmission locks up in high gear

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch failure can cause the vehicle to become difficult or impossible to shift, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the transmission cooling system can cause the transmission to overheat, leading to premature wear, damage, or failure, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.

symptoms: Rust spots or corrosion on the vehicle's body
flexing of rack and pinion steering.
